---
/**
 * Reusable retainer CTA box.
 * Mirrors wiki/snippets/retainer-cta.md content, restyled with site brand tokens.
 */
---

<aside class="retainer-cta">
  <div class="retainer-cta__inner">
    <p class="retainer-cta__eyebrow">Zamana Programları</p>
    <h3>Claude'u şirketinize entegre edelim.</h3>
    <p>
      Bu wiki'yi okudunuz, ama tek başına okumak yetmez. Zamana, Claude'u kurumsal düzeyde uygulamak için iki program sunuyor:
      <strong>Bireysel Program</strong> (3 hafta birebir, $1.000) veya
      <strong>Kurumsal Retainer</strong> (3 ay × 6 çalışan, $9.000).
    </p>
    <div class="retainer-cta__actions">
      <a href="/programlar/" class="btn btn--primary">Programları İncele</a>
      <a href="/iletisim/" class="btn btn--ghost">Görüşme Talep Et</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .retainer-cta {
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--c-navy) 0%, var(--c-navy-deep) 100%);
    color: var(--c-text-light);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--c-gold);
    box-shadow: var(--sh-mid);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .retainer-cta__inner {
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
  }
  .retainer-cta__eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-gold-light);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .retainer-cta h3 {
    color: var(--c-white);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .retainer-cta p {
    color: var(--c-text-light-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .retainer-cta strong {
    color: var(--c-text-light);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .retainer-cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
